@startuml Inventory State Machine
title Inventory Item - State Machine Diagram
left to right direction

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor#E0F7FA
    BorderColor#00838F
    ArrowColor#424242
}

[*] --> AVAILABLE : Product created\nwith stock

AVAILABLE --> RESERVED : Order placed\n(stock reserved)
AVAILABLE --> QUARANTINE : Quality issue flagged
AVAILABLE --> SOLD : Direct sale\n(no reservation)
AVAILABLE --> DISCONTINUED : Product discontinued

RESERVED --> SOLD : Order paid\n(reservation confirmed)
RESERVED --> AVAILABLE : Order cancelled\n(reservation released)
RESERVED --> QUARANTINE : Damaged during fulfillment

SOLD --> RETURNED : Item returned\n(good condition)
SOLD --> QUARANTINE : Item returned\n(needs inspection)

QUARANTINE --> AVAILABLE : Quality approved\n(restocked)
QUARANTINE --> DAMAGED : Quality failed\n(mark as damaged)
QUARANTINE --> RETURNED : Customer return approved

RETURNED --> AVAILABLE : Processed return\n(restocked)
RETURNED --> SOLD : Relisted as new

DAMAGED --> [*] : Written off\n(discarded/recycled)
DISCONTINUED --> [*] : Removed from system

' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' NOTES
' ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

note right of AVAILABLE
  Available for purchase
  Visible in catalog
  Stock count accurate
end note

note right of RESERVED
  Held for pending order
  Not available for others
  Reserved for 30 minutes
end note

note right of QUARANTINE
  Under inspection
  Not available for sale
  Awaiting quality decision
end note

note right of RETURNED
  Customer return
  Quality verified
  Can be restocked
end note

@enduml
